cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the development of safe artificial general intelligence (AGI) and proposes the use of distributed ledger technology (DLT) to ensure alignment of AGI values and goals with human values. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of DLT for security and auditing purposes, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Additionally, the proposal involves the use of decentralized applications (dApps) and smart contracts, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
